Package: zenodomanageR
Title: Interface to Zenodo API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Guillermo", "Porriños", email = "grmo.prieto@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to manage Zenodo depositions and files via API, including: (1) get deposition ID using deposition names; (2) deposition creation; (3) draft creation and deletion; (4) file upload and deletion; (5) publish depositions; (6) polling for status; (...) others.
